# Notification Feature Implementation Plan

## Goal Description
The user questioned the purpose of the "Notifications" toggle. Currently, it only toggles a visual state. The goal is to give it a tangible purpose by implementing a simulated notification system (Toast messages) that reinforces habit completion or provides "reminders" when enabled.

