### User Explanation
- Explain that in a real app, this would use Push API.
- For this web app, we will simulate it by showing encouragement messages or "Top of screen" banners when the user returns.

## Verification Plan

### Manual Verification
1.  Go to Profile.
2.  Toggle Notifications "On".
3.  Expect a visual confirmation (Toast/Alert) saying "Daily reminders set for 9:00 AM".
4.  Reload app -> Setting should persist.
